---
title: Honey Mustard Chicken with Baked Veggies
description: In this recipe, we’re DIY-ing our way to a honey mustard sauce that's leagues better than the bottled stuff—add in a pinch of garlic and a splash of white wine vinegar and boom! You've got it made. Here, we’re using it to coat chicken breasts, then reducing it to a satisfyingly sticky glaze. Filled out with roasted zucchini, sweet potatoes, and red onions, the whole dish comes together in a symphony of sweet and savory.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/au-honey-mustard-chicken-b086044d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/au-honey-mustard-chicken-6728f818.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: Australian
